Steps:
------

1. Go to netplan directory.

  $ cd /etc/netplan/ 

2. Open the .yaml file using a text editor.

  $ sudo vi 50-cloud-init.yaml

3. Change the file as shown below;
dhcp4: false
addresses:
  - 192.168.1.100/24
routes:
  - to: default
    via: 192.168.1.1
nameservers:
  addresses:
    - 8.8.8.8
    - 192.168.1.1
